        "timestamp": "2018-08-20 00:47:44.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\n> (1 comment)\n\nIt seems to be logically correct, however originally the code was:\n((servers.size() == 1 && (\"\".equals(servers.get(0)))) || (servers == null) || (servers.isEmpty())) in line 399 BusConsumer.java\nI guess, there should not be any side effect by making it >= 1",
